Elevate Your Hand Care Experience With York Street Spa

At York Street Spa, we believe that well-groomed hands and beautiful nails are a reflection of your overall confidence and style. Our manicure services are designed to pamper your hands and nails, leaving them looking and feeling their absolute best.

Spa manicure:

$55

Deluxe manicure:

$75

Express manicure:

$30

biosculpture manicure:

$85

biosculpture with nail extension:

$110

add-on shellac:

$18

add-on SHELLAC removal:

$10

add-on paraffin treatment:

$25

Spa Manicure

At York Street Spa, we believe that your hands deserve the utmost care and attention. Our manicure services are designed to provide you with not just beautiful nails but a pampering experience that leaves your hands feeling rejuvenated and your confidence elevated.

Your Gateway to Relaxation

Our Spa Manicure is more than just a nail treatment; it's a luxurious experience that nourishes your hands and nails from the inside out. From the moment you settle into our serene environment, you'll be transported to a world of tranquility.

What to Expect with Our Spa Manicure

Nail Shaping:

Our skilled technicians will shape your nails to perfection, ensuring they are even and well-groomed.

Cuticle Care:

We gently care for your cuticles, ensuring they are soft and well-maintained.

Exfoliation:

A soothing exfoliation treatment will remove dead skin cells, leaving your hands feeling silky-smooth.

Hydration:

Your hands and nails will be treated to a deeply moisturizing massage, promoting healthy, hydrated skin.

Nail Polish:

Choose from a wide range of high-quality nail polishes to add the finishing touch to your manicure.

Our Spa Manicure is not just about aesthetics; it’s about taking a moment for yourself and indulging in self-care. As you leave our spa, your hands will not only look stunning but also feel revitalized and refreshed.

Our Spa Manicure Services

Deluxe Spa Manicure

Elevate your hand care experience with our Deluxe Spa Manicure, which includes extra indulgent treatments for a truly pampering session.

Refresh Polish Express Mani

Perfect for those on the go, our Refresh Polish Express Manicure ensures a quick and beautifully polished look.

Gel BioSculpture Mani

Enjoy the long-lasting beauty of Gel BioSculpture Manicure, known for its durability and vibrant colors.

Paraffin Wax

Rejuvenate your hands with our Paraffin Wax treatment, which deeply moisturizes and soothes your skin.

Soak Off

Safely remove your existing nail polish with our Soak Off service, leaving your nails ready for a fresh look.

Soak Off and Overlay

Combine the removal of old polish with an overlay for a renewed and enhanced appearance.

Soak Off and Manicure

Start with a clean slate as we remove old polish and pamper your nails with a manicure.

Gel with Extension

Achieve the length and style you desire with our Gel Manicure with Extension service.

Add-On

French Manicure:

Add a classic touch to your manicure with French polish.

Nail Art:

Express your creativity with our Nail Art add-on, featuring intricate and unique designs.

Nail Repair:

For damaged nails, our Nail Repair service will restore strength and vitality.

Treat yourself to a manicure at York Street Spa and experience the perfect blend of relaxation and nail care. Our skilled technicians and high-quality products ensure that your hands and nails are pampered to perfection.

Book an appointment with our talented manicurists and let your hands do the talking!
